Package de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.desires

Record Class ActionInfo

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.desires.ActionInfo
public record ActionInfo(eis.iilang.Action value, String info) extends Record
The Record ActionInfo provides a data structure to store an Action combined with additional information about the reasoning process. In Addition it provides static methods to generate ActionInfo instances for the Actions accepted by the massim 2022 simulation.
Author:
Heinz Stadler, Melinda Betz (minor contribution)
